Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.35,0:02:05.60,OPCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}所以千萬不要隨手丟棄
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.14,0:02:05.98,OPCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\frz13.829\pos(867,67)}不能放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.98,0:02:08.60,OPCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這顆滿載夢想的心靈
